{
  "stem": "322.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And before she leaves, and if I'm still in the bedroom-- you know, in fact, a lot of times, she'll leave and I'm still half asleep.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She'll leave for me articles of interest.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And in 1980, it was just unbelievable, these, these, these denials.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "All a sudden these, these, these, like, you know, Jews are angered because there is another view of some sort.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then here comes this offer of a $50,000 reward to anyone who could prove that Jews were gassed in gas chambers at Auschwitz or that gassings took place, something to the effect.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And they didn't mean to offer it to specific individuals, to anyone.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I left it alone.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I wasn't going to touch it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And my wife kept leaving those articles again, as if to say, aren't you going to do something about it?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Well, I wasn't about to do anything about it other than write a letter to the editor, which I did.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I wrote and about three, four newspapers published that letter to the editor in which I expose them to be what they are, a bunch of old Nazis, neo-Nazis or whatever, you know, and that's it.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, soon after that letter was published.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And it was also published in the international edition.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Suddenly I get a letter marked personal, right here to my office, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and it says, Dear Mr.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Mermelstein, from a letter to the editors, we are convinced that you can prove the Jews were gassed in gas chambers in Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now-- and in this letter, they go back by stating that they had this offer to anyone, but, but they, they, they went ahead and, and, and dismissed it, and-- but now we want to renew that $50,000 reward for you, Mr.",
      "word_count": 42
    }
  ],
